    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-spec icon featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile feedback and mechanical purity. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the double VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. While the exterior displays a light patina from enthusiasts' use, the chassis dynamics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and cross-drilled rotors. A mechanically sound example of BMW's high-water mark in naturally aspirated engineering.",
      "price": 38500.0,
